Subject: windows report policy
Description: Hello Team we have to set git in windows report policy but its content block by policy for your reference please find the screenshot,
What_We_Know__c:
- git was getting blocked by a report only policy
- enabled stealthy DPI and it worked correctly
- server: 5.9.4.1
- client: 6.2.4.0054
Solution_Comment__c:
GIT blocking was solved by enabling Stealthy DPI from Device Control -> Global Settings.

The CAP reporting issue is being investigated under ticket no. 00434661
